ed="T" n="0858c12"/><anchor n="T.50.2061.0858c12"/><head><date from-iso="+0936-12-05" key="j20632662067017" to-iso="+0947-03-14">晉</date><placeName key="PL000000042886"><placeName>鳳翔府</placeName><placeName>法門寺</placeName></placeName><persName key="A013472">志通</persName>傳</head><p><lb
ed="T" n="0858c13"/><persName key="A013472">釋志通</persName>，俗姓<name>張</name>氏，<placeName key="PL000000042848">右扶風</placeName>著姓家之子也。早<lb
ed="T" n="0858c14"/>知<anchor xml:id="beg0858sgsz37"/><choice resp="sgsz"><sic>遣</sic><corr>遺</corr></choice><anchor xml:id="end0858sgsz37"/>世<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1929"/>，克務淨門，選<anchor xml:id="beg0858sgsz39"/>禮<anchor xml:id="end0858sgsz39"/>名師，登于上品，諸<lb
ed="T" n="0858c15"/>方講肆，遍略留心。後<date key="j20261062052491" notBefore-iso="+0835-03-10" notAfter-iso="+0907-06-06"><name>唐</name>之季</date>，兵革相尋，自此<lb
ed="T" n="0858c16"/>駕已東巡<ptr target="#n2273"/>。薄遊<ptr type="glossary" target="#g674"/><placeName key="PL000000023581">洛下</placeName>，遇<persName key="A023065">嚩日囉三藏</persName><ptr target="#n2934"/>，行瑜<lb
ed="T" n="0858c17"/>伽教法<ptr type="glossary" target="#g93"/>，<persName key="A013472">通</persName>禮事之<ptr target="#n2936"/>。乃欲陟<placeName key="PL000000014411">天台</placeName>、<placeName key="PL000000031276">羅浮</placeName>，遂辭。<lb
ed="T" n="0858c18"/><ref type="person" target="#A023065">三藏</ref>曰：「<ref type="person" target="#A023065">吾</ref><anchor xml:id="beg0858sgsz41"/>此<anchor xml:id="end0858sgsz41"/>求翻譯，屬<placeName key="PL000000000214">中原</placeName>多事。<ref type="person" target="#A013472">子</ref>議南<lb
ed="T" n="0858c19"/>征奈何路梗何？」<persName key="A013472">通</persName>曰：「泛天塹其如<ref type="person" target="#A013472">我</ref>何？」<lb
ed="T" n="0858c20"/><ref type="person" target="#A023065">三藏</ref>曰：「苟去<placeName key="PL000000009925">吳</placeName>、<placeName key="PL000000013265">會</placeName>間，可付之<name>梵</name>夾，或緣會<lb
ed="T" n="0858c21"/>傳譯。」<persName key="A013472">通</persName>曰：「已聞命矣。」以<date key="j20640502064433" notBefore-iso="0939-01-28" to-iso="0940-02-15"><name>天福</name>四年<anchor xml:id="beg0858sgsz43"/>己<anchor xml:id="end0858sgsz43"/>亥歲</date>，<lb
ed="T" n="0858c22"/>天王錫命于<placeName key="PL000000008355">吳越</placeName>，遂附海艦達<placeName key="PL000000008355">浙</placeName>中。時<persName key="A006771"><persName>文<lb
ed="T" n="0858c23"/>穆王</persName><persName>錢<roleName>氏</roleName></persName></persName>奉朝廷之故，具威儀樂部，迎<persName key="A013472">通</persName><lb
ed="T" n="0858c24"/>入府庭供養，於<placeName key="PL000000011485">真身塔寺</placeName>安置，施賚豐腆。<lb
ed="T" n="0858c25"/><persName key="A013472">通</persName>請往<placeName key="PL000000014411">天台山</placeName>。由是登<placeName key="PL000000014519">赤城</placeName>，陟<placeName key="PL000000014412">華頂</placeName>，既而<lb
ed="T" n="0858c26"/>於<placeName key="PL000000014700">智者道場</placeName>挂錫。因覽《西方淨土靈瑞傳》<ptr target="#n2935"/>，<lb
ed="T" n="0858c27"/>變行迴心，願生彼土，生常不背西坐。山中<lb
ed="T" n="0858c28"/>有<placeName key="PL000000014498">招手石</placeName>者，昔<persName key="A001301">智顗</persName>夢其石上有僧臨海<lb
ed="T" n="0858c29"/>上舉手相招召之狀。<persName key="A001301">顗</persName>入<placeName key="PL000000014411">天台</placeName>見其僧名<pb ed="T" n="0859a" xml:id="T50.2061.0859a"/><lb
ed="T" n="0859a01"/><persName key="A004834">定光</persName>，耳輪聳上過頂，亦不測之神僧也。乃<lb
ed="T" n="0859a02"/>相見，乃問<persName key="A001301">顗</persName>曰：「還記得相招致否？」<persName key="A001301">顗</persName>曰：「唯。」<lb
ed="T" n="0859a03"/>此石峻<anchor xml:id="beg0859sgsz1"/>峙<anchor xml:id="end0859sgsz1"/>，顧下無地。<persName key="A013472">通</persName>登此投身，願速生<lb
ed="T" n="0859a04"/>淨土。奮軀而墮一大樹中，枝軟幹柔，若有<lb
ed="T" n="0859a05"/>人扶接焉，殊無少損。乃再叩榼投之，落<lb
ed="T" n="0859a06"/>于巖下蒙茸草上，微有少傷，遲久蘇矣。眾<lb
ed="T" n="0859a07"/>僧謂為豺虎所啖，及見其猶殗殜<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1930"/>然，<anchor xml:id="beg0859sgsz3"/>舁<anchor xml:id="end0859sgsz3"/>就<lb
ed="T" n="0859a08"/>本道場。初<persName key="A013472">通</persName>去不白眾，遂分人各路尋覓，<lb
ed="T" n="0859a09"/>至<placeName key="PL000000014645">螺溪</placeName>，民村有巫者言事多驗，或就問焉。<lb
ed="T" n="0859a10"/>神曰：「<ref type="person" target="#A013472">伊僧</ref>在西南方，現有金鎧神扶衛不<lb
ed="T" n="0859a11"/>死，我到彼神氣盡矣，固難近也。」皆符協<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1931"/>神<lb
ed="T" n="0859a12"/>言。後往<placeName key="PL000000011566"><placeName>越州</placeName><placeName>法華山</placeName></placeName>，默修淨業，將欲化去，<lb
ed="T" n="0859a13"/>所止房地生白色物，如傅粉焉<ptr target="#n669"/>。未幾，坐禪<lb
ed="T" n="0859a14"/>床而終，遷座闍維，有五色煙覆于頂上，<placeName key="PL000000011566">法<lb
ed="T" n="0859a15"/>華<choice resp="sgsz"><sic>川</sic><corr>山</corr></choice></placeName><ptr target="#n2939"/>中咸聞異香焉。</p><p xml:id="pT50p0859a1601"><lb
ed="T" n="0859a16"/>系曰：昔<persName key="A013473">薄拘羅</persName>有五不死<ptr target="#n2937"/>，今<persName key="A013472">通<roleName>公</roleName></persName>二不死；<anchor xml:id="beg0859sgsz5"/>昔<anchor xml:id="end0859sgsz5"/><lb
ed="T" n="0859a17"/><persName key="A005937">法充</persName>投千仞<placeName key="PL000000018778">香爐峯</placeName>而不亡<ptr target="#n2938"/>，<persName key="A013472">通</persName>且同矣。得<lb
ed="T" n="0859a18"/>非天龍負翼不損一毛乎？而能延彼連持<lb
ed="T" n="0859a19"/>色心<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1932"/>未斷者何？俾其增修淨土業耳。</p>
